# --- Confidentiality guard: never commit private source recordings ---
# A document rendered from a private or confidential recording (its video,
# transcript, or frames) is a LOCAL correctness proof only and must never
# enter this repo. Keep private test inputs and their renders out.
*_private*
lanes/sop/output/
lanes/**/output/private/

# --- Local scratch / temp ---
scratch/
scratchpad/
tmp/
*.tmp
*.bak
*.orig
*.log

# --- Local working notes (never publish) ---
# Session notes, handoffs, reviews, reconciles, research, and planning are
# internal records, not deliverables.
_SESSION_NOTES*.md
_HANDOFF*.md
_REVIEW_*.md
_RECONCILE_*.md
_RESEARCH_*.md
_planning/

# --- Python ---
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.egg-info/
.venv/
venv/
env/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# --- Brand design staging (local source only) ---
# Raw exports from the design pass. The SHIPPED assets are copied into
# _config/ (brand.css, brand/logo/*) and assets/brand/, which ARE tracked.
_assets-content-engine-brand/
_design-content-engine/

# --- Renderer intermediate ---
# build_pdf writes a .src.html that Chrome prints from; regenerated every
# render, never a deliverable. Matches anywhere (samples + the render selftest).
*.src.html

# --- Render byproducts not meant to ship ---
# Stage output/ folders carry .gitkeep but their generated contents are
# run-local. Commit only the deliverables under samples/rendered/.
lanes/**/stages/**/output/*
!lanes/**/stages/**/output/.gitkeep
00-install/output/*
!00-install/output/.gitkeep
!00-install/output/readiness-scorecard.example.md
